div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Lucky Day</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Thursday</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Lucky Colors</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 ring-1 ring-slate-200\">#F7DC6F</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 ring-1 ring-slate-200\">#E6B34D</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 ring-1 ring-slate-200\">#F8B14D</span></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Lucky Stone</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900\">Tiger Eye</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Life Path Number</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">5</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 rounded-3xl bg-amber-50 p-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Numerology meaning:</span> <!-- -->The name Zain is believed to have numerological significance, with a life path number of 5. This number is associated with the themes of adventure, change, and progress. People with this number are often seen as free spirits, and are drawn to new experiences and challenges. They are also natural communicators and problem solvers, and have a strong desire to explore and learn.</div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Personality</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Personality Traits</h2></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">Kind</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">Just</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">V</span></div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-text h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H19a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v18a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H6.5a1 1 0 0 1 0-5H20\"></path><path d=\"M8 11h8\"></path><path d=\"M8 7h6\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Spiritual</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Spiritual Significance</h2></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-amber-50 p-4 text-slate-800 leading-7\">In Hadith, Prophet Muhammad (pbuh) mentioned Zain as a name for those who strive to purify their intentions and actions, and give generously to others.</div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Cultural Context</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Cultural Significance</h2></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-slate-700 leading-7\"><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4\">The name Zain carries a rich cultural heritage, recognized and respected among various Islamic communities. It signifies qualities of leadership, strength, and resilience, dating back to the days of early Islamic history where prominent figures bearing the name Zain, such as Zain al-Abidin, the fourth Shia Imam, held important spiritual and political roles.</div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4\">Spiritually, the name Zain is deeply steeped in the treasured values of kindness, generosity, and selflessness. As such, the personality of those named Zain is seen as a reflection of God&#x27;s immense generosity and benevolence towards humankind, inviting them to emulate these beautiful qualities in their daily lives.</div><p class=\"rounded-3xl bg-emerald-50 p-4 text-sm text-emerald-800\">Traditional Islamic naming context<!-- --> — Traditional Islamic name with deep spiritual significance in Islamic culture</p></div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Popularity</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Popularity by Region</h2></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4 text-slate-700 leading-7\"><div class=\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-slate-200 last:border-0\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Saudi Arabia</span><span class=\"text-slate-600\">Score: <!-- -->78</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-slate-200 last:border-0\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Pakistan</span><span class=\"text-slate-600\">Score: <!-- -->71</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-slate-200 last:border-0\"><span class=\"font-medium\">UAE</span><span class=\"text-slate-600\">Score: <!-- -->70</span></div></div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Famous People</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Famous People and Real-World Usage</h2></div></div><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500 mb-3\">Historical Figures &amp; Cultural References</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-100 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">Zain Jabarah Al-Abidin</span><span class=\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-100 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">Zain Malik</span><span class=\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-100 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">Zain al-Abidin (son of Imam Hussein)</span></div></section><section class=\"nv-card-solid\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-languages h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m5 8 6 6\"></path><path d=\"m4 14 6-6 2-3\"></path><path d=\"M2 5h12\"></path><path d=\"M7 2h1\"></path><path d=\"m22 22-5-10-5 10\"></path><path d=\"M14 18h6\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Translations</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Name Translations</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500\">Additional language translations available for this name.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"nv-card-solid p-4\"><div class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\"><span>🇺🇸</span><span>English</span></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Zain</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\">beauty, adornment, or handsome</p></div><div class=\"nv-card-solid p-4\"><div class=\"mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\"><span>🇵🇰</span><span>Urdu</span></div><p class=\"font-